        <div class="container">
          <div class="cta-box reveal">
            <div>
              <h3>Whitelist access. Premium standard. Serious roleplay.</h3>
              <p>
                Capital Roleplay is being positioned as a cleaner and more refined FiveM experience for players who want custom content, stronger immersion, and a server identity with actual direction.
              </p>
            </div>

            <a class="button" href="#apply">Start Application</a>
